KUWAIT CITY , April 8 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- Representatives of the Health Ministries of the Gulf Cooperation Council -LRB- GCC -RRB- states today held a meeting in Riyadh to discuss preventive measures against the mad cows disease .
Director of the Public Health Department at the Kuwaiti Public Health Ministry Rashed al- Owayesh said before the meeting that the participants would discuss <ENAMEX TYPE="OKAY">precautionary measures for the GCC members to take so as to prevent the spreading of mad cows disease into the Gulf region .</ENAMEX>
